Class AbstractRectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • pythagoras.d.RectangularShape
      • pythagoras.d.AbstractRectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, IRectangle, IRectangularShape, IShape
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Rectangle

    public abstract class AbstractRectangle
extends RectangularShape
implements IRectangle
    Provides most of the implementation of IRectangle, obtaining only the location and dimensions from the derived class.

        public PathIterator pathIterator(Transform t,

        Description copied from interface: IShape

        pathIterator in class RectangularShape
